description: Following the tremendous success of our first Pre-Fractal Mint. The most successful to date. We are excited to announce the Season 2 Mint of Maneki on Fractal, which will take place directly on Fractal Bitcoin. This highly anticipated mint, hosted on the Bipolar platform, is here to reward those who love to be rewarded. Maneki Neko is here to bless your wallets! Known as the "beckoning cat" of fortune, it symbolizes luck, wealth, and prosperity. With Season 2 Mint on Fractal Bitcoin, let the power of brand new collection of Maneki Neko bring endless rewards straight to you! First is First.
